  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of Prostaglandin I2 analogue use on the
      development of chronic allograft nephropathy and changes in allograft function in prevalent
      renal transplant recipients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
